406
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,360
 Jesam.

407
00:30:01,360 --> 00:30:02,960
 Baci me dolje.

408
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:05,120
 Baci me dolje.

409
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:06,180
