411
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:08,480
 Dao je sve.

412
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:09,460
 Ako je dao sina,

413
00:30:09,460 --> 00:30:10,940
 kako nam onda sa svim,

414
00:30:10,940 --> 00:30:11,880
 s njim,

415
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,300
 neće dati sve ostalo.

416
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:14,700
 Zato nemojte ograničavati Boga

417
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:15,900
 i nemojte ga stavljati.

418
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:16,960
 Plan B.

419
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:17,460
 Amen.

420
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:28,900
 Di mi Petra.

421
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:31,600
 Pobjegla je.

422
00:30:31,600 --> 00:30:32,200
 Vratite.

423
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:32,540
 Evo je.

424
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:34,220
 Još jedna stvar.

425
00:30:34,220 --> 00:30:34,920
 Petra, dođu.

426
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,540
 Jedan pljesak.

427
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:36,540
 Aplauz.

428
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:44,620
 Petra nije mogla biti

429
00:30:44,620 --> 00:30:46,040
 kada smo primali nove članove.

430
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:56,780
 pa sam odlučio iznenaditi.

431
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:57,740
 Svaki put zaboravimo,

432
00:30:57,740 --> 00:30:59,040
 rekao danas ćemo to napraviti.

433
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:01,280
 Petra će danas potpisati ovdje,

434
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:02,140
 pred vama sada.

435
00:31:02,140 --> 00:31:03,220
 Imaš puno više svjedoga

436
00:31:03,220 --> 00:31:03,940
 nek što su oni imali.

437
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:05,680
 Sve će o prisegu.

438
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:06,700
 Sad ne mora čitat,

439
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:07,860
 ali ovdje će potpisat.

440
00:31:09,280 --> 00:31:10,320
 Ali o čemu se radi?

441
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:12,380
 Da će cijeniti zajedništvo,

442
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:14,240
 da će to biti visoka vrijednost

443
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:16,600
 i da ćemo raditi na tome u timu

444
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:19,240
 i da će za to dat snagu, dragi Bog.

445
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,440
 Tako da je potpisala.

446
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,340
 Imamo sad nizini potpis.

447
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:22,640
 I dobit će potvrdu

448
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:25,320
 kao član zajednice,

449
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:26,540
 tako da čistitam ti Petra

450
00:31:26,540 --> 00:31:27,380
 sada i službeno.

451
00:31:33,220 --> 00:31:34,420
 E, čekaj, čekaj.

452
00:31:34,420 --> 00:31:38,520
 A da te opremimo za tvoju službu,

453
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:40,140
