454
00:31:40,140 --> 00:31:42,100
 Isu je rekao, ne nosite kese.

455
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:43,760
 Danas nosimo kese.

456
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:46,120
 Tako da unutra ti je novi zavijet

457
00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:47,920
 i bilježnica da možeš pisat bilježke

458
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:49,120
 i učit, kao svi ostali

459
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:51,480
 koji imaju ovdje bilježnice naši članovi.

460
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,300
 Nema nikola, nema veze.

461
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:54,580
 Tako da ti je to starter kit,

462
00:31:54,580 --> 00:31:56,800
 starter paket za službu.

463
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:58,460
 Ja još jedan bljesak.

464
00:32:03,220 --> 00:32:07,260
 Ako radimo ozbiljno,

465
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,300
 onda mora biti službeno.

466
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:10,680
 Tako da smo to htjeli napraviti.

467
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,580
 Sada će biti pauza.

468
00:32:11,580 --> 00:32:12,640
 Prije nego što bude pauza,

469
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:13,720
 dozvolite mi još nešto.

470
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:15,520
 Znate Nedjeljka koju sam spomenuo.

471
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:19,880
 E, jeste išli kad u Međugorje,

472
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,460
 ali ste ono putovali cijelu noć

473
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:24,020
